{"tid":118380,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得早睡早起已經過時？","createTime":"2017-02-13T03:40:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-13T08:02:56.000Z","uid":28,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27fff38130f13d2b5322b7848248bad81c465e9a","tid":118380,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:40:07.000Z","msg":"以前老一輩成日話遲訓遲起身會浪費左大半日，但而家好似變左太早訓覺反而會miss左更加多野，到你朝早起身睇番已經遲左"},{"pid":"13209955a8bb544606335ae180e63d6cad42dd7d","tid":118380,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:41:33.000Z","msg":"Yes 慣左遲睡早起"},{"pid":"e171169e47ce31f0fdd50eaca10da0ba5f0c2dd3","tid":118380,"uid":71913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T03:59:34.000Z","msg":"睡眠重質不重量"},{"pid":"c52b33f8d784cb7db67b5669a9039ef71a3378b4","tid":118380,"uid":18384,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:03:09.000Z","msg":"咩十一點前訓，五六點起身，成功人士最鍾意吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93d10a287f569a0c84c3b44a9b9a65338452ae84","tid":118380,"uid":50786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:08:47.000Z","msg":"早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64037a586de761180f95c65eeb711c920db64a49","tid":118380,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T04:59:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩十一點前訓，五六點起身，成功人士最鍾意吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n早排仲係咁吹奏唔知咩連續30日朝早4點起身 challenge <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6078c7babccc6095561a1079fa36439983b26a2e","tid":118380,"uid":28,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:00:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果已經慢慢調節左生理時鐘，個影響會唔會無咁大？"},{"pid":"599a4e5c6e1376508277b99b25e8fa350eee42c5","tid":118380,"uid":79403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:04:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽左咁耐都冇人解釋到"},{"pid":"0b9f3639ea3108c6f8cf005131782301cfae918a","tid":118380,"uid":7998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:16:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果已經慢慢調節左生理時鐘，個影響會唔會無咁大？</blockquote><br />\n以前我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲同我屋企人爭論 我2點瞓10點起咪同我11點瞓7點起身咪一樣瞓8個鐘 根本無分別<br />\n但經過我呢幾個月因爲要返placement 焗住早睡早起 （我唔夠瞓會頭痛）<br />\n發覺就算都係瞓足8個鐘 早睡早起係會精神好多 同埋皮膚好左勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：純粹個人經歷 無咩科學研究support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"598422fbefc7b2719e93d22ef487b403aed0bd0d","tid":118380,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:20:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽左咁耐都冇人解釋到</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔知點解釋, 但到左30歲打後就一定覺<br />\n影響好大<br />\n<br />\n利申:返夜超過10年"},{"pid":"bb387cbe66d0f6594c8ec15a2f4a7148f170d393","tid":118380,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:21:20.000Z","msg":"一係定時二先係早睡早起"},{"pid":"b83660dc83ff1e02143d5790dab8547101bf6931","tid":118380,"uid":47091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:24:19.000Z","msg":"子時三刻<br />\n11點左右熟睡個肝先排到毐<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">好似係</span></span>"},{"pid":"98437f3883528a342dd53f482026bd4027bfebf0","tid":118380,"uid":65433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:24:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽左咁耐都冇人解釋到</blockquote><br />\n聽中醫講好似十點/十一點係肝部運作排毒的最佳時間，如果瞓緊覺係最理想"},{"pid":"7e85b5a6fcdf6789f923bbff55476af62a27a9ad","tid":118380,"uid":29167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:25:41.000Z","msg":"1點左右瞓，7點9 起身 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1a3c2fd049791f1afb76cb94cdc16d45f21d345","tid":118380,"uid":6880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:30:07.000Z","msg":"7點起身 <br />\n無論係11點訓 定係1點訓 結果都係唔夠訓"},{"pid":"01ebc8e938dd8e9cb14936a723c821508744466c","tid":118380,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:30:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知發育期果陣早訓好撚重要，決定左你以後既身高"},{"pid":"d01c348176ea1efbb11671d6c14f87fb6b7563cc","tid":118380,"uid":30751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知發育期果陣早訓好撚重要，決定左你以後既身高</blockquote><br />\n早睡早起同均衡飲食係有幫助<br />\n但遺傳先係決定身高既重點?<br />\n<br />\n利申9up"},{"pid":"d5d0092a4961b10c29fb513f0b5452aa49cbca35","tid":118380,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:34:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果已經慢慢調節左生理時鐘，個影響會唔會無咁大？</blockquote><br />\n以前我都係咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲同我屋企人爭論 我2點瞓10點起咪同我11點瞓7點起身咪一樣瞓8個鐘 根本無分別<br />\n但經過我呢幾個月因爲要返placement 焗住早睡早起 （我唔夠瞓會頭痛）<br />\n發覺就算都係瞓足8個鐘 早睡早起係會精神好多 同埋皮膚好左勁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：純粹個人經歷 無咩科學研究support<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nreal<br />\n依家都逼自己較番個生理時鐘<br />\n想皮膚好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a3a359f1f4e8558959d494a4bbc957167033c6","tid":118380,"uid":7109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:44:10.000Z","msg":"有時候晚上做嘢會有效率啲，但通常都係差啲<br />\n反而早起身通常會比較好<br />\n<br />\n所以呢啲真係睇人，冇金科玉律"},{"pid":"c17bb6c0788c1b9fca090cd7e959b82c125eb1ee","tid":118380,"uid":49853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:48:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我知發育期果陣早訓好撚重要，決定左你以後既身高</blockquote><br />\n早睡早起同均衡飲食係有幫助<br />\n但遺傳先係決定身高既重點?<br />\n<br />\n利申9up</blockquote><br />\n七成遺傳三成後天(好似係)"},{"pid":"c5af70978f54dbd94725bf06feed10879aa02025","tid":118380,"uid":1049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:49:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩十一點前訓，五六點起身，成功人士最鍾意吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n11點先放工，第二日六點又起身準備返工<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6d3b88ebb795d98187862606c107038df5cefdb","tid":118380,"uid":24024,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T05:51:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咩十一點前訓，五六點起身，成功人士最鍾意吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老先有既睡眠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d04043f4e52cd8e7685769bed15a4d1f9314eb51","tid":118380,"uid":29273,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:01:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咩十一點前訓，五六點起身，成功人士最鍾意吹奏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n廢老先有既睡眠時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試過一排十一點瞓<br />\n但都係八點起身<br />\n係精神既<br />\n但一諗到要返工又頹返<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fd10d3f1a48721020b3fa0ade2a027747364d48","tid":118380,"uid":34955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:02:25.000Z","msg":"身體好唔好唔知<br />\n但早瞓第二日堅精神好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e913d28bd17bf47dcdcf9b9157358214b3ffe328","tid":118380,"uid":22693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>早訓對身體好啲就一定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聽左咁耐都冇人解釋到</blockquote><br />\n聽中醫講好似十點/十一點係肝部運作排毒的最佳時間，如果瞓緊覺係最理想</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個肝識睇鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解會知時間"}]}